ANASTASIO A. YLAGAN v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 45948]

[Ante, p. 294;

322 U. S. 763]

Statute of limitation; the statute is not tolled by failure of other remedies.

Decided March 6, 1944; petition dismissed on defendant’s motion. Opinion, page 294, ante.

Plaintiff’s petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court June 12, 1944.
